OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FWorkers for a green energy company
OL,7,Fplanning new electricity pylons across
OL,8,FWales risked spreading disease among
OL,9,Fcattle by entering lands "under active
OL,10,Fbovine TB restrictions", the High
OL,11,FCourt has heard.
OL,13,FNatalie Barstow, the Campaign for the
OL,14,FProtection of Rural Wales and the Land
OL,15,FJustice Coalition are taking legal
OL,16,Faction against Green Generation Energy
OL,17,FNetworks Cymru over how the firm is
OL,18,Fcarrying out its proposed new project.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
