OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FThe campaigners say the company has
OL,7,Facted unlawfully in not giving proper
OL,8,Fnotice when visiting land and failing
OL,9,Fto take adequate steps to prevent the
OL,10,Fspread of disease.
OL,12,FThe campaigners say this was a risk to
OL,13,Fprotected species and people's
OL,14,Flivelihoods.
OL,16,FGreen GEN Cymru is defending the legal
OL,17,Fclaim, which relates to a network of
OL,18,Felectric cables being built across
OL,19,FWales on pylons and underground.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
