PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FSasha Blackmore KC, for the
OL,7,Fcampaigners, said in written
OL,8,Fsubmissions to a High Court hearing in
OL,9,FCardiff on Tuesday that Green GEN
OL,10,FCymru was "promoting a project the
OL,11,Fscale of HS2" across more than 200km
OL,12,F(124 miles) of Wales.
OL,14,FShe told the court it served notice to
OL,15,Fenter land for surveys in August 2024
OL,16,Fand turned up "without telling people"
OL,17,Fmore than 15 months later to gather
OL,18,Fdata ahead of compulsory purchase
OL,19,Forders.
OL,26,@rD@KOUsD@MO]xD@OOUxD@fO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
