PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FThe barrister said that the company
OL,7,Frisked spreading animal diseases
OL,8,Facross the area.
OL,10,FShe said: "The defendant enters in
OL,11,Fvisibly dirty and non-disinfectable
OL,12,Fclothing/footwear; without adequate
OL,13,Fpolicies for biosecurity or health or
OL,14,Fsafety and even with out-of-date
OL,15,Finadequate insurance.
OL,26,@rD@KOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
