OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,F"The defendant has been photographed
OL,7,For recorded doing so in land under
OL,8,Factive bovine TB restrictions, in
OL,9,Fbadger setts, in SSSI (sites of
OL,10,Fspecial scientific interest) land and
OL,11,Fwatercourses housing globally
OL,12,Fendangered protected species
OL,13,Fvulnerable to inadequate disinfection
OL,14,Fwith no evidence of qualified
OL,15,Fecologists."
OL,17,FShe said that farmers were "worried to
OL,18,Fleave their farms" in case workers
OL,19,Ffrom the company turned up in their
OL,20,Fabsence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@LO]yD@\OUzD@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
