PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FThe campaigners are seeking a
OL,7,Fdeclaration that Green GEN Cymru has
OL,8,Facted unlawfully, while Ms Barstow,
OL,9,Fwho believes an outbreak of bovine TB
OL,10,Fon her family farm may have been
OL,11,Fcaused by surveyors, is seeking
OL,12,Fdamages.
OL,14,FPhilip Coppel KC, for the company,
OL,15,Fsaid in written submissions that
OL,16,F"there is no evidence of any causal
OL,17,Flink between the defendant's surveys
OL,18,Fand any biosecurity issue".
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
