OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FHe said the campaigners seemed to want
OL,7,Fto use the claim to stop the pylon
OL,8,Fproject, where the "principal
OL,9,Fobjective is delaying the projects in
OL,10,Fthe hope that they may go away
OL,11,Faltogether".
OL,13,FHe described the approach to the claim
OL,14,Fas "a mess", with complaints about
OL,15,Fdirty boots and lack of notice "being
OL,16,Fcherry-picked" in "an emotive and
OL,17,Fpartial manner".
OL,26,@pD@TOUsD@KO]vD@DOUvD@KO]wD@`OUxD@NO]xD@
OL,26,ASOUyD@OO]
