PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FMr Coppel added that there was
OL,7,F"considerable opposition" to the work
OL,8,Fbeing carried out, the importance of
OL,9,Fwhich he said "cannot be overstated"
OL,10,Fin helping to meet the Government's
OL,11,Fdecarbonisation goals.
OL,13,FHe said: "One respect in which this
OL,14,Fhas been manifested is in seeking to
OL,15,Fresist access for carrying out surveys.
OL,17,F"This has necessitated applications
OL,18,Ffor warrants where it has been clear
OL,19,Fthat access cannot be obtained without
OL,20,Fthe use of force."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@YO]qD@OOUqD@dO]uD@JOUyD@AOU|D@
OL,26,ARO]
