OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FThe barrister said: "The claimants
OL,7,Fdescribe these projects as being the
OL,8,Fsame scale as HS2 but this is a
OL,9,Fmeaningless comparison since HS2 is a
OL,10,Frailway line; they are electricity
OL,11,Flines carried on pylons, poles or, in
OL,12,Fshort sections, underground.
OL,14,F"They will no doubt have material
OL,15,Fvisual effects on the areas through
OL,16,Fwhich they pass, but the defendant
OL,17,Fpromotes the projects on the basis
OL,18,Fthat such effects are demonstrably
OL,19,Foutweighed by the benefits of the
OL,20,Fprojects, and by the greater risks of
OL,21,Fdoing nothing."
OL,26,@nD@UOUvD@AOU}D@OO]
