OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FThe hearing, before Mr Justice
OL,7,FKimblin, is due to conclude on
OL,8,FWednesday.
OL,10,FWhat are the political parties saying
OL,11,Fabout the building of pylons?
OL,13,FA Welsh Conservative spokesperson said
OL,14,Fthe party's roadmap is about
OL,15,F"transform(ing) our economy while
OL,16,Fprotecting our unique national
OL,17,Fheritage.
OL,26,@wD@KpmwD@Opn
