SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FThey continued: "We will introduce a
OL,7,Fmoratorium on industrial-scale solar
OL,8,Fand wind farms to protect the Welsh
OL,9,Fcountryside and adopt a 'bury cables
OL,10,Ffirst' approach to infrastructure in
OL,11,Fthe Welsh countryside."
OL,13,FA Reform Wales spokesperson said the
OL,14,Fparty is "absolutely" against the
OL,15,Findustrialisation of the countryside.
OL,17,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"Generating more renewable energy is
OL,19,Fkey to reaching our net zero targets
OL,20,Fbut a just transition must be built
OL,21,Fwith communities, not imposed on them.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
