PN,46912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FThe party said it would "immediately
OL,7,Fprohibit the use of large steel
OL,8,Flattice pylons for new 11-132 kV lines
OL,9,Fin Wales, with a clear presumption in
OL,10,Ffavour of undergrounding and overhead
OL,11,Falternatives permitted only where
OL,12,Finstallation is via low wooden poles
OL,13,For equivalent, less intrusive
OL,14,Finfrastructure."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
