PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776949868
OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FA Welsh Labour spokesperson said that
OL,7,Fthe policy it established while in
OL,8,Fgovernment was that, "where possible,
OL,9,Fnew power lines should be laid
OL,10,Funderground. But this needs to be
OL,11,Fbalanced against cost that could make
OL,12,Fprojects that create good jobs and
OL,13,Flower energy bills unviable."
OL,15,FThey added: "We will ensure that
OL,16,Frenewable energy projects benefit the
OL,17,Fcommunities that host them, and that
OL,18,Fthey work to protect Wales from
OL,19,Funstable global energy markets."
OL,26,@wD@MOU
