OL,3,CClean energy firm risked spreading
OL,4,Cbovine TB, High Court told
OL,6,FLeader of the Welsh Liberal Democrats
OL,7,FJane Dodds said the party supports the
OL,8,Ftransition to renewable energy, but
OL,9,Fsays "it must be done in a way that
OL,10,Fworks with communities, not against
OL,11,Fthem."
OL,13,FShe added: "We are clear that wherever
OL,14,Fpossible, electricity infrastructure
OL,15,Fshould be undergrounded rather than
OL,16,Frelying on vast networks of pylons
OL,17,Fcutting across some of Wales' most
OL,18,Fbeautiful landscapes.
OL,20,FThe Green Party has also been
OL,21,Fapproached for comment.
OL,26,@uD@LOU
